  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects must be willing and able to provide written consent on the EC approved
             Informed Consent form.

          -  Subjects must require a lens power from 15 to 30 diopters.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with any anterior segment pathology for which extracapsular
             phacoemulsification cataract surgery would be contraindicated.

          -  Subjects with corneal pathology potentially affecting topography.
      </textblock>
